page.title: 05BROWNIES
page.content: WE HAVE BROWNIES AT {CARLTON LODGE} EVERY WEDNESDAY 6.15pm. TO 7.15pm. WE HAVE TO PAY SUBS EVERY WEEK OF 25P.OUR BROWN OWL IS CALLED JENNY THOMPSON AND HER MUM HELPS HER.TWO GUIDES COME BECAUSE THEY ARE DOING SERVICE FLASH.WE HAVE DIFFERENT SIXES,ELVES,SPRITS,KELPIES AND IMPS.I AM IN ELVES.WE HAVE TWO TEDDY BEARS.ONE IS CALLED SNOWIE OWL AND THE OTHER IS CALLED CRESTED OWL.WE HAVE DIFFERENT BADGES THAT WE WORK FOR.THERE IS THE FOOTPATH,ROAD AND HIGHWAY BADGES.WE PLAY GAMES WITH THE {BROWNIES}.WE GO ROUND THE LAKE.SOMETIMES WE COLLECT THINGS WHEN WE WALK ROUND.WE GO ON PACK HOLIDAYS EVERY YEAR.THE FIRST TIME I WENT AWAY TO CASTLETON.THE SECOND TIME TIME WE WENT TO THE LONG HOUSE, CARLTON LODGE.I GO TO 1ST CARLTON MINIOTT BROWNIES.
